    "en": {
      "title": "6 diaspora organizations banned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Defense has taken steps to lift the ban on six diaspora organizations that were designated as banned organizations in Sri Lanka.",
        "Thus, the Ministry of Defense says that the ban on six organizations namely the Australian Tamil Congress, the Global Tamil Forum, the World Dravida Coordination Committee, the Dravida Eelam People's Federation, the Canadian Tamil Congress and the British Tamil Forum has been lifted."
      ],
